('Celebrity Face Dance', 1291, '&amp;laquo;Celebrity Face Dance&amp;raquo; - an exciting game for girls that combines makeup and dancing. In this game, you can transform into real stars and experience being a makeup artist and dancer at the same time. Three celebrities await you - Ariana, Taylor and Billie, each with their unique style and image. Choose your favorite star and start creating a unique look for her. Use various cosmetic products to enhance beauty and individuality girls. Then, when the makeup is ready, move on to the most exciting part - the dance! Follow the instructions on the screen and mimic the celebritys moves to become a true dance floor star!', 'Depending on the gaming device a computer mouse click or a simple touch on touch screens is used for control', 'English'),
