('Ellie And Friends Get Ready For First Date', 1452, 'Join Ellie And Friends Get Ready For First Date! Explore chic ensembles, trendy accessories, and glamorous styles to make a lasting impression. Dive into the excitement of the first date as these fashion-forward friends set the trend for the perfect look. Elevate your style game, embrace the thrill of romance, and let Ellie and Friends guide you through a fashionable journey to a memorable first date. Make every moment stylish and unforgettable!', 'Left Mouse Button Click', 'English');
