('Battlefield Brawl Co op Challange', 1467, 'Are you ready for the soldiers duel? Choose the weapon and character that suits you best. Start the duel in normal game mode or mayhem game mode!', 'Player 1 W A S D Movement Space Fire Player 2 Arrow Keys Movement P Fire When you enter the game from a mobile device you can use the touch controls on the screen', 'English'),
('Memory Match Magic', 1468, 'Dive into the enchanting world of Memory Match Magic, a delightful casual game that challenges your memory and takes you on a magical journey of matching pairs! Immerse yourself in a whimsical realm filled with colorful cards, charming animations.', 'Memory Match Magic is a classic memory matching game with a magical twist The objective is simple yet engaging ndash flip and match pairs of cards to reveal the magical wonders hidden beneath With each successful match you unlock a bit of the enchant', 'English'),
